name: Sikuliator
body:
# Sikuliator
Sikuliator is a system for automatic execution of GUI tests distributed across many machines, backed by SikuliX.
It is developed by Malte Schledjewski as a part of his studies at the Hochschule Kaiserslautern 
in collaboration with the Fraunhofer Institute for Industrial Mathematics ITWM.
